1304
00:57:28,880 --> 00:57:31,880
This is not new particles, which are not quarks.

1305
00:57:31,880 --> 00:57:33,880
This is just a subheading

1306
00:57:33,880 --> 00:57:35,880
here, quarks and then things underneath.

1307
00:57:35,880 --> 00:57:38,880
There are up quarks, down quarks.

1308
00:57:38,880 --> 00:57:39,880
Why are they up and

1309
00:57:39,880 --> 00:57:40,880
down and not up and down?

1310
00:57:40,880 --> 00:57:43,880
There's nothing up and down about them.

1311
00:57:43,880 --> 00:57:49,880
What direction?

1312
00:57:49,880 --> 00:57:50,880
Up and down?

1313
00:57:50,880 --> 00:57:52,880
Up and down means in the Earth's gravitational field.

1314
00:57:52,880 --> 00:57:55,880
There's nothing upy or downy about them.

1315
00:57:55,880 --> 00:57:57,880
Then it gets worse.

1316
