It gets more silly.

1319
00:58:04,880 --> 00:58:07,880
There are charm quarks, which are charming, I suppose.

1320
00:58:07,880 --> 00:58:09,880
I don't know.

1321
00:58:09,880 --> 00:58:12,880
Then there are, now this is, if you don't,

1322
00:58:12,880 --> 00:58:17,880
if you're squeamish or very,

1323
00:58:17,880 --> 00:58:22,880
bottom quarks, bottom quarks.

1324
00:58:22,880 --> 00:58:27,880
Bottom quarks and then top quarks.

1325
00:58:27,880 --> 00:58:30,880
The symbols are, of course, exactly the same.

1326
00:58:30,880 --> 00:58:32,880
I just didn't feel like writing the words.

1327
00:58:32,880 --> 00:58:35,880
Up, down, strange, charm, bottom, top.

1328
00:58:35,880 --> 00:58:37,880
Isn't there a beauty and truth?

1329
00:58:37,880 --> 00:58:39,880
Same as bottom and top.

1330
00:58:39,880 --> 00:58:42,380
I got a little pretentious beauty

1331
00:58:42,380 --> 00:58:44,880
and truth, so bottom and top.

1332
00:58:44,880 --> 00:58:47,880
Strange and charm.

1333
00:58:47,880 --> 00:58:51,880
How and under what circumstances these

