things were named is not interesting.

1335
00:58:55,880 --> 00:58:56,880
I don't know.

1336
00:58:56,880 --> 00:58:59,880
I do know, but never mind.

1337
00:58:59,880 --> 00:59:00,880
They're all fermions.

