fields as you use for the particles.

1347
00:59:29,880 --> 00:59:32,380
And there's no completely coherent

1348
00:59:32,380 --> 00:59:34,880
convention that everybody sticks to.

1349
00:59:34,880 --> 00:59:35,880
All right, they're all fermions.

1350
00:59:35,880 --> 00:59:37,880
The whole lot of them are fermions.

1351
00:59:37,880 --> 00:59:38,880
As I said.

